{"tid":275431,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"呢度有冇人大汗撚？","createTime":"2017-06-08T04:31:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-31T14:43:19.000Z","uid":44747,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ab10aeb373b0c198d6e48b114ced3524cbaf5f88","tid":275431,"uid":44747,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T04:31:47.000Z","msg":"有冇人同我一樣一到夏天就好大汗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n姐係就算唔做運動就咁行路都會流好大汗<br />\n眼見街上啲人冇流好大汗，見到自己咁樣就會好尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋啲汗淹左成日都唔舒服，同成身又痴立立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想問睇中醫有冇效解決到？定係我平時唔做開運動所引致"},{"pid":"c3c64796898ac2e9093af8499cdf08eeb9ade047","tid":275431,"uid":44747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T04:35:02.000Z","msg":"補充下 我經常飲凍野會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48310b984976f772cb6e5e2356b9c58d3a1856d9","tid":275431,"uid":19300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T04:38:48.000Z","msg":"冬天坐係到都流晒汗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42dc8706ee4071175345fcb9295f2fca2ce97da2","tid":275431,"uid":44747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T04:39:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冬天坐係到都流晒汗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n癲過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d1c1f462a9042234ac6077a4114f3b382dd1d5a","tid":275431,"uid":64464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T04:45:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>冬天坐係到都流晒汗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n癲過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌我都係<br />\n一熱少少就成身汗<br />\n本身汗唔臭<br />\n但愈出愈多就勁大陣味<br />\n搞日除左返工平日都唔會出街"},{"pid":"243a82412edf9676d50245428917e1b62ab54e10","tid":275431,"uid":4418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T04:53:43.000Z","msg":"我都好易出汗，應該係肝火盛"},{"pid":"facd03f202723e7cef522cb8109174f058169ef5","tid":275431,"uid":46753,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T05:10:10.000Z","msg":"開住冷氣訓教照出汗"},{"pid":"2b32a1695421aeb5c3c1568d28efae0948722423","tid":275431,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T05:12:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>開住冷氣訓教照出汗</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6945ae43c703752840c8f4606e3e62642a622464","tid":275431,"uid":91244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T05:13:21.000Z","msg":"+1<br />\n坐車嘅時候周圍嘅人已經會自己走開<br />\n有咩解決方法?"},{"pid":"199bb9b95fa5652d69b68069887d3a53409550ec","tid":275431,"uid":3434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T05:16:04.000Z","msg":"好憎夏天 屋企行5分鐘去地鐵站都出晒汗<br />\n依家隨身帶住包紙巾"},{"pid":"c65b5ac0d813e43ba51363c56120f95bd28d31cd","tid":275431,"uid":29487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T05:16:19.000Z","msg":"成日飲凍野會特別怕熱   最好小飲 <br />\n利申：戒唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b31cb614b00bd63bc0e1f88cbec0135becdb7670","tid":275431,"uid":895,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T05:19:03.000Z","msg":"大汗肥仔揮手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9136484bf58cfb7d796bfc372c6b6a6ffed17cde","tid":275431,"uid":105545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T05:20:05.000Z","msg":"落街行去對面馬路個地鐵站已經岀汗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59071380d2e3d1b62a65962ae4671f51b4ca21ff","tid":275431,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T05:20:46.000Z","msg":"人大 汗撚"},{"pid":"870d6b346a6de5ac2fa169dc2395d9be5a933cab","tid":275431,"uid":29438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T05:22:55.000Z","msg":"大汗到出街著白色衫露撚晒點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b7d045b218b0e13841b488d53804d0216238cd5","tid":275431,"uid":94828,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T05:24:23.000Z","msg":"係北極都出哂汗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c74da77421146cf59b61a3cf4f21aa7b6e003d66","tid":275431,"uid":61300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T05:28:32.000Z","msg":"成吉思汗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08a7f74634212e10a20fa4da038399729f765c9a","tid":275431,"uid":35516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T05:28:51.000Z","msg":"真係有苦自己知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"312fd8e206d83085990cd9fd8d8aced5ed071d56","tid":275431,"uid":86337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T05:30:07.000Z","msg":"慘得過我剩係個頭出汗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 行10分鐘好似游完水咁"},{"pid":"7537e3621f00f0a2512dc11c0153ca40502ba793","tid":275431,"uid":104294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T05:33:50.000Z","msg":"未出門口，已經出汗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff70cd70443003cfe1b0cb12b0e1b0d37804b9ad","tid":275431,"uid":88260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T05:34:44.000Z","msg":"行一陣個人出晒水 乾左個人又臭到仆街"},{"pid":"de742ec4cef7223865658575ecebf6b791ee755d","tid":275431,"uid":34023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T05:37:11.000Z","msg":"here<br />\n著到啲衫臭晒<br />\n屌佢老母"},{"pid":"b34068134d8c7895fb1d17404901f5da8a629d0f","tid":275431,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T05:48:37.000Z","msg":"我食個拉麵 飯都出汗 <br />\n唯一解決 慢慢食 食到佢凍凍地 <br />\n出街 冇解決 後生果陣有位同事同我講 同我一樣大汗 所以揸車 所以我努力搵錢揸車"},{"pid":"ae902a2e804879d70215a6e7e160a08327f1d27b","tid":275431,"uid":47621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T05:55:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>+1<br />\n坐車嘅時候周圍嘅人已經會自己走開<br />\n有咩解決方法?</blockquote><br />\n我以前出汗都好撚臭 <br />\n去買盒無患子磨砂沖涼後用<br />\n止汗水晶出門前濕水搽格肋底 背脊位 <br />\n加埋u記吸汗背心 汗會照出 但冇咩味<br />\n不過跑步出勁多都點都會有少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2c88ff043fd3b1c1da6389416e3ac2caa94fcf6","tid":275431,"uid":89166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T06:01:07.000Z","msg":"跑完步好似游完水咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n行路就無乜汗"},{"pid":"532a56cbc21f9f1aae8eaf26fa046d9451dd5214","tid":275431,"uid":118766,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T06:07:25.000Z","msg":"萬寧定屈臣有支止臭野 搽左會照出汗但無味 叫做好過無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57383c73cc00d094ead135d9ee5fb3564c10a952","tid":275431,"uid":44747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T06:10:48.000Z","msg":"睇黎好多巴打都同病相憐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我自己上網睇話可以食玉屏風散,但當然成效就唔知有冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8924b14102c61e8f42402ad582c2a2193ddb5c2d","tid":275431,"uid":67516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T06:12:41.000Z","msg":"次次一出汗就好似游完水咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"001fcb6327e807d66588d3db36ec6de912e695ae","tid":275431,"uid":68445,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T06:15:57.000Z","msg":"沖完涼未出門口背脊果浸水抹完五秒又有一浸"},{"pid":"4bd5131c1bf82302bd634baeb2515f52d6f69a2b","tid":275431,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T07:14:07.000Z","msg":"我對濕度好敏感，一焗雨我D汗就浮曬出嚟好似一粒粒黃豆咁"},{"pid":"dbdb312b6595c8046514289bae94a1069f5b80ea","tid":275431,"uid":89166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T07:17:01.000Z","msg":"呢度有冇中醫可以解釋下點解咁大汗... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋有冇得醫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86803505d81866109f993be6086126ef11fc23a7","tid":275431,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T07:23:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>萬寧定屈臣有支止臭野 搽左會照出汗但無味 叫做好過無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實有唔小呢d 偏鹼性"},{"pid":"a2027ad2453ac6a9c1631b1256f2f4af2e52b257","tid":275431,"uid":9741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T07:27:37.000Z","msg":"大汗撚留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日濕住真係好唔舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06c178bdeed6e1a26d47305dbeab3f83d85a1576","tid":275431,"uid":39431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T07:30:33.000Z","msg":"呢幾日只要係戶外多過一分鐘一定出汗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07841408b6f4003af1ceb3eb73269eb57898ad1e","tid":275431,"uid":12497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T07:39:24.000Z","msg":"個身超撚大汗<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6ed422bc448d0c571d4894479e51c60fee234e2","tid":275431,"uid":56833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T07:41:02.000Z","msg":"近排打得丁多搞到大汗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c830ecc91161a24377a6251f041666b407ebfbf","tid":275431,"uid":59654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T07:42:05.000Z","msg":"冬天都出 唔好講夏天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d8aece42091c31e873c4e5423c2b5a8518f7e29","tid":275431,"uid":64797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T07:44:25.000Z","msg":"大汗到飛天<br />\n每一日條孖煙囪都係濕晒<br />\n落左地鐵行少過5分鐘既路番公司都會濕晒<br />\n仲要俾啲亞姐串9我做乜咁健康做完運動先番工"},{"pid":"cc44ce33d9e7d61dd4043f7c99eebc66d8ff1b1b","tid":275431,"uid":73256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T07:45:59.000Z","msg":"唉 留名"},{"pid":"c615732c6c951d88ecb648f6c25ce77161a7cf41","tid":275431,"uid":20205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T07:46:50.000Z","msg":"夏天一出門口即出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去到冷氣地方 要停幾分鐘d汗先識停<br />\n冬天一焗即出汗 由其係d鋪頭冬天唔開冷氣 焗撚到死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64dfc6603e75756ada46ee4d876024bec259aaf1","tid":275431,"uid":20736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T07:54:56.000Z","msg":"平時好大汗<br />\n手同液下都易出汗<br />\n有時著完啲白衫唔係即時洗 好快著多幾次就唔著得<br />\n因為個格拉底黃晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3e1b30b1a4814df8dfb8e2565f1d1dc2e007e1f","tid":275431,"uid":64047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T08:16:08.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n去親旅行都唔行得遠, 去星加坡一出門口即刻成件tee濕撚晒<br />\n<br />\n著底衫就連個頭都溶埋咁滯, 越著越熱惡性循環<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔想掉老婆假, 減肥出多d日間汗等身體適認吓會好d<br />\n<br />\n利申: 阿雪式中央大肚腩"},{"pid":"02c978ca1dc410155a401c7bbace4c309380b1b1","tid":275431,"uid":8528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T09:55:52.000Z","msg":"我都好撚大汗 誇張到短衫短褲踢拖出街5分鐘 成個背脊額頭都係汗。我唔認為係中醫肝火盛事 應該係天生汗腺分泌勁 啲汗唔係臭 但就不停標汗唔識停咁 <br />\n。本身我都做開運動 爆汗感覺好正。但如果正常社交出街著去街衫出汗就好煩"},{"pid":"d24