/>\n<br />\n唯一慶幸係除非汗流浹背，否則唔臭嘅"},{"pid":"dcf4be167571f7606976dcc89b63298cb1938d50","tid":275431,"uid":3434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T13:50:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/10/005831_25d80376a385dedd9e7dedd83cfd3fa1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F10%2F005831_25d80376a385dedd9e7dedd83cfd3fa1.jpg&h=c5600b19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前cap落但一直未試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n位置中晒 仲有個背<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n反而個頭無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f49c27234b5dd269a77e06b23daf27d63eb4e56d","tid":275431,"uid":1998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T14:07:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有無大汗絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前行返學可以出汗出到條校裙濕哂<br />\n啲汗多到係大脾流落小腿 頭到頸到啲汗流落胸到再加埋胸到本身啲汗就搞到胸前又濕一撻<br />\n一返課室坐低就會成張凳濕哂 起返身仲可以有攤汗係凳到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搞到返到課室都唔敢坐低要企到乾/抹完先坐<br />\n大汗得好過份 係熱一陣啲汗直情會係頭滴落地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以好怕曬好怕熱 因為知自己會出汗出得好勁<br />\n唔敢成日去户外玩怕俾人笑 又驚話熱俾人話港女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身唔熱見到我都覺得熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好彩既係自己無乜汗味 但都唔想出街俾人見到自己件衫濕哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我同你一樣，瘦你dd,  但平日坐個pat都流汗，搞到條褲/ 裙痴住個人，搞到個人坐立不安咁，而係大脾流汗落小腿真係好唔舒服。<br />\n開住冷氣都會流汗，心情激動又流汗，瞓覺又流汗，更莫講出街，我再熱d會用蛇粉搽多汗位再出街。<br />\n<br />\n唯一慶幸係除非汗流浹背，否則唔臭嘅</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa446e7fbaabe936581408f137bc9c4288e59c57","tid":275431,"uid":23592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"